    <div class="home-text">
      <h1>INTRODUCTION</h1><br />
      <p>
        Ever work at a workplace where there are just so many engineers and different teams that cross collaboration between them become difficult?  Or think back when you were that new intern with all these questions, but was not sure who to ask?  It doesn't stop there, we've all been in that situation where you've got a question, but the answer seems like something you should already know - so you hesitate.  Or maybe you're stuck in that 'loop' of "go ask this person" and that person tells you to 'go ask that person' and so on...<br /><br />

        Fact is we've all faced this situation at some point or another.  Not only does this hurt productivity and efficiency, but it creates divisions throughout a company, which can harm team collaboration and innovation, project management, and prevent knowledge sharing from one team to the next.<br /><br />

        TeamChat is a messenging application used to, not change your company or work culture, but instead, help unify existing ones and provide more opportunities for collaboration and interaction.  Keep reading to find out what makes our application so special!
      </p>
